parameters:
Thanks to you magical girls, this city, no... the
world is being protected. We must express our
gratitude.
Is it Lumi? Well, I don't know...
I wonder if she has returned here?

No, she left a while ago and hasn't come back
since. Lumi is an adopted child, but we didn't see
eye to eye. By the way, what about you?

Ah, well, someone said they wanted to deliver a
letter but it seems like it didn't reach them, so
I brought it instead.

Sigh. Is it that guy...? It's troublesome, isn't
it... Anyway, Lumi won't be coming back here
anymore.
Yeah... I don't have any idea where she went...

Seems like you're really interested in shady work.
I don't know for sure, but you might be going
underground or something... Honestly...

S-Sorry, I have a hard time with young women like
you. I appreciate the magical girl, but I have a
trauma and it's too much for me.
ピッキングで解錠する

If you have a \C[2]lock-picking tool\C[0] and a
\C[2]hairpin\C[0], you might be able to challenge
unlocking the door...
盗むレベルによってコモンを変更する
ここで単品アイテム入手
I have a bad feeling about this.
